ion\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kipchoge, who was the two-time defending Olympic champion pariticpating in his fifth Olympics, is now 39 years of age.\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kipchoge\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"his fifth Olympics\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"39 years\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And his struggles here follows a 10th place in Tokyo, leaving an uncertain future in the sport after failing to complete the distance for the first time in his career.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1436, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.975486601777382, \"rank\": 0.025127205543937946, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his struggles\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"a 10th place\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"an uncertain future\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1350}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"the distance\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"his career\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had a pain in my back at about 20km and decided not to finish and try to get out,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pain\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"my back\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"about 20km\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The hills did not affect me at all.\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The hills\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pain made me stop.\\\"\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pain\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I walked for 2km and had more than 300 people on either side of me walking with me.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"2km\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1612}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 300 people\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1641}, {\"ngram\": \"either side\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why I do not have my shirt, the socks, the shoes, the race number.\\\"\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my shirt\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"the socks\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"the shoes\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1735}, {\"ngram\": \"the race number\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kipchoge accepted his 'DNF' was part of the event and \\\"that's life,\\\" before making a comparison with boxing.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kipchoge\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"his 'DNF\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1792}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1822}, {\"ngram\": \"a comparison\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today was a tough day at the office.\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Today\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1872}, {\"ngram\": \"a tough day\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"the office\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can train for a very long time but one day, it can happen,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very long time\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's like boxing.\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can go to a training camp for five months and be knocked out in two seconds.\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a training camp\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"five months\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2043}, {\"ngram\": \"two seconds\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But life will continue.\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is my worst marathon.\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2131, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my worst marathon\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never done a DNF [did not finish].\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a DNF\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's life.\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like a boxer, I have been knocked down, I have won, I have come second, eighth, 10th, fifth - now I did not finish.\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a boxer\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's life.\\\"\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2316, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans started to question whether Kipchoge will race the distance again, but Kipchoge has not rushed to make any decision, with a rest next to decide what he will do 11 years after switching to the 26.2-mile distance.\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fans\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2322}, {\"ngram\": \"Kipchoge\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"the distance\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"Kipchoge\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2402}, {\"ngram\": \"any decision\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2438}, {\"ngram\": \"a rest\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"11 years\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"the 26.2-mile distance\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not want to comment on what will happen tomorrow.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to try to evolve - if I do not evolve, then I do other things,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other things\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know what my future will hold.\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my future\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will think about it over the next three months.\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next three months\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I still want to try to run some marathons.\\\"\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some marathons\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kipchoge could be seen gifting fans his shoes and vest after stepping off the course, while he also knocked back pleas from his fellow runners to push through the pain.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kipchoge\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2817}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2844}, {\"ngram\": \"his shoes\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"pleas\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2927}, {\"ngram\": \"his fellow runners\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2951}, {\"ngram\": \"the pain\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The other runners were telling me to push on,\\\" Kipchoge revealed.\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 3045, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The other runners\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"Kipchoge\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I was telling them, 'No, I have pain, I can not'.\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I could feel the love and respect from them.\\\"\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the love\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3122}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kipchoge could be seen at the finish line, following a lift from officials, with fans flocking to greet the legendary Kenyan.\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3273, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kipchoge\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3156}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3189}, {\"ngram\": \"a lift\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3207}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3222}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3233}, {\"ngram\": \"the legendary Kenyan\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kipchoge then gifted his vest to a young supporter before attending to his media duties.\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kipchoge\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3283}, {\"ngram\": \"his vest\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3304}, {\"ngram\": \"a young supporter\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3325}, {\"ngram\": \"his media duties\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please